&lt;p>Proves knowledge of discrete logarithm $x$ such that $y = g^x$:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>TypeScript SDK</title><link>https://casiojapi.github.io/tongo-docs-ui/docs/tongo-sdk/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://casiojapi.github.io/tongo-docs-ui/docs/tongo-sdk/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="tongo-typescript-sdk">
 Tongo TypeScript SDK
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#tongo-typescript-sdk">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>The &lt;code>tongo-sdk&lt;/code> provides a high-level TypeScript interface for building applications with confidential payments. It abstracts away cryptographic complexity while providing full access to Tongo&amp;rsquo;s features.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="installation">
 Installation
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#installation">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>npm install tongo-sdk
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="quick-start">
 Quick Start
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#quick-start">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">import&lt;/span> { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Account&lt;/span> } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">from&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;tongo-sdk&amp;#39;&lt;/span>;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Create account from secret key
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">const&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">account&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">new&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Account&lt;/span>(
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">secretKey&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Private key (bigint or Uint8Array)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;0x123...tongoAddress&amp;#39;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Deployed Tongo contract
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">provider&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Optional: Starknet RPC provider
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">&lt;/span>);
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">console&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">log&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">account&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">tongoAddress&lt;/span>());
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Output: &amp;#34;5mJNv2Z8QxFfKw7hL3e9P1rT6sY4pQ2nX8kM7dR3cB1&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;hr>
